      <title>卢拉称央行不能为市场服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/lula-says-central-bank-can-t-be-at-the-service-of-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦加大了对巴西央行的攻击力度，称由行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托领导的央行需要真正实现自主，而不应被金融市场“拥有”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/lula-says-central-bank-can-t-be-at-the-service-of-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
